channel.title: 377 (dds speced base) CLIENTS WITH GODSWORD REAL GODSWORD STANCES + SPECIAL'S?
channel.description:
Hmm.... I don't know how.. but somehow i just cant make it.. Someone know's how i can do it? I think i used dds-speced base i tought it was 377 right? or 317.. PLEASE SOME one help me!?!?!?
Okay, well i found one, tried it.. But d-claws don't work and grafix of all the pvp stuff and everything DOESN'T WORK! please some one teach me how to do it. or someone make a client it can use, my server p-scape is pretty populair but if i get gs stance's i get more ppls to stay :D,
help me, you will be rewarded.
Sorry, java :P.
--- addd one day ater.
okay i searched for all the delta clients and i tried a few off them. But when i download them and i un-zipped them, i try to run, all works. the next step: log-in, works! the final bug.. SPAZ.. if i log in i see a name look like "awe2a241d" or something, verry weird. also my head is doing weird... how come? and if you found a client you think it must work with gs stances + d claws ect, please send me moparscape link.
Thanks.
-Mod P
